Package troops

Class Troop

java.lang.Object
troops.Troop
Direct Known Subclasses:
Archer, Cavalry, Mage, Warrior
@Entity public abstract class Troop extends Object
The abstract class representing the different troops. This abstract class serves as a template for the different troops in the game.
